dict.string:
Interactive Tutorial
The tutorial is an interactive Scrivener project that walks you through getting started with Scrivener. Because you are free to edit the tutorial project, you will work with a copy which will be saved to your hard drive.
Should you ever want to reset the tutorial to get rid of any changes you have made, simply delete the copy on your hard drive and then select "Interactive Tutorial" from the Help menu to create a fresh copy.
Click on "Continue..." to choose where to save the tutorial project. The tutorial will then be opened automatically.
